            </div>
            <div class="stl_view" >
                <div class="stl_05 stl_06">
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 0.5183em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_07 stl_08 stl_09">第</span><span class="stl_07 stl_08 stl_09">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_09">2</span><span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0239em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_07 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0239em;">章</span><span class="stl_07 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.75em;">&nbsp;设备物理连接 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 2.9661em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_12">云管理平台的企业账户建立之后，现在可以进行设备的连接了，本章节主要介绍设备的接口和具 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 4.2661em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">体的连接方法。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 6.2882em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_09">2-1</span><span class="stl_14 stl_08 stl_09">、电源连接 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 8.6828em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">电源连接采取 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">DC</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">、凤凰端子两种接入方式，直流 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">24V </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">电压、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">1A </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">电流供电。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 17.4632em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_09">2-2</span><span class="stl_14 stl_08 stl_09">、指示灯说明 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 19.8578em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">※</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09">POWER</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">：电源指示灯，电源接通之后红灯长亮。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 21.4161em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">※</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09">DEV</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">：设备指示灯，设备接入正常能通信，绿灯长亮。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 23.6907em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 23.6907em; left:9.6986em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_16" style="word-spacing:-0.024em;">：互联网接通指示灯，在无线中继或者 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_16" style="word-spacing:-0.024em;">4G </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_16" style="word-spacing:-0.024em;">的场合绿灯偶尔闪一下信号最强，而绿灯闪得越 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 25.5745em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.012em;">快表示信号越弱；在 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.012em;">PPPoE</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.012em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.012em;">DHCP </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.012em;">的场合正常联网后绿灯长亮。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 35.6549em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_09">2-3</span><span class="stl_14 stl_08 stl_09">、设备接入 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 38.0495em; left:7.4833em;z-index:260; "><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">配置 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">LAN</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">（以太网）、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">RS232</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">RS485</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">USB </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">四种接口，可以采取任何一种方式接入 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">PLC</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_17" style="word-spacing:-0.0093em;">、 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 39.3495em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09">HMI</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">、机器人、视觉等设备。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 49.5364em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09">2-3-1</span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_09">、以太网方式连接 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 51.8245em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0138em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0138em;">的 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0138em;">LAN </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0138em;">口通过网线与设备的 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0138em;">RJ45 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0138em;">网口连接，可连接 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0138em;">4 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0138em;">台以太网接口设备。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 59.4114em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0245em;">2-3-2</span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0245em;">、</span><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0245em;">RS232 </span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0245em;">方式连接 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 61.6995em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">与设备通过 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">RS232 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">串口连接。考虑网络通讯的效率，参数设置为：</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">115200</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">8</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">1</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">N </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_20" style="word-spacing:-0.0286em;">方式。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 62.9995em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0119em;">下面以欧姆龙 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0119em;">PLC </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0119em;">为例。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stl_02">
