                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 15.2364em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0245em;">2-3-3</span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0245em;">、</span><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0245em;">RS485 </span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0245em;">方式连接 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 17.5245em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.0015em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.0015em;">与设备通过 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.0015em;">RS485 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.0015em;">串口连接（</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.0015em;">RS485 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_21" style="word-spacing:0.0015em;">扩展模块要改成半双工）。考虑网络通讯的效率，参数 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 18.8245em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">设置为：</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">115200</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">8</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">1</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">N </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">方式。下面以欧姆龙 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">PLC </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0159em;">为例。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 39.0995em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0123em;">另外，</span><span class="stl_23 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0123em;">RS485 </span><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0123em;">扩展模块如果是全双工，还要改成半双工，半双工的跳线设置如下（以欧姆龙 </span><span class="stl_23 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0123em;">PLC &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 40.3995em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0122em;">的 </span><span class="stl_23 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0122em;">RS485 </span><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0122em;">扩展模块为例）： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 60.9864em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0254em;">2-3-4</span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0254em;">、</span><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0254em;">USB </span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0254em;">方式连接 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 63.2745em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0146em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0146em;">与 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0146em;">PLC</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0146em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0146em;">HMI </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0146em;">通过 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0146em;">USB </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0146em;">连接。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
