                <div class="stl_05 stl_06">
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 0.5715em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_13 stl_08 stl_09">2-4</span><span class="stl_14 stl_08 stl_09">、外网设置 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 2.9661em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24">SS700</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0375em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0375em;">支持</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0018em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0018em;">DHCP</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:0.2244em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0018em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:0.2244em;">PPPoE</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:0.2244em;">、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:0.2244em;">WiFi</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0378em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0378em;">中继、</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0378em;">4G</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0377em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0377em;">四种外网连接方式，并采用</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0018em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0018em;">WAN</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0377em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_24" style="word-spacing:-0.0377em;">叠加技术。初始默 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 4.2661em; left:5.7333em;z-index:76; "><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_25">认为</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_25" style="word-spacing:0.0714em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_25" style="word-spacing:0.0714em;">DHCP</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_25" style="word-spacing:0.0475em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_25" style="word-spacing:0.0475em;">的自动方式（自动</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_25" style="word-spacing:0.0714em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_25" style="word-spacing:0.0714em;">IP</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_25" style="word-spacing:0.0714em;">）。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 5.8245em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_26" style="word-spacing:-0.05em;">以初始默认的方式连网时，</span><span class="stl_23 stl_08 stl_26" style="word-spacing:-0.05em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_26" style="word-spacing:-0.05em;">与上级路由通过网线连接即可，连网成功后，显示出的具体信 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 7.1245em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_09">息如下图： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 20.8828em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">选择初始默认以外的连网方式时，</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">SS700 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">通过任一 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">LAN </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">口与电脑直连，浏览器输入 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">192.168.200.1 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 22.1828em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">访问</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">智能远程模块管理后台</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">，默认密码为：</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">admin</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">。（建议采用 </span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">IE10.0 </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing:-0.0074em;">以上版本）各种连网方式的设 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 23.4828em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">置如下： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 26.0112em; left:9.5434em;"><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">也可以用电脑、手机、</span><span class="stl_29 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">pad </span><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">通过无线网络连接 </span><span class="stl_29 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">SS700</span><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">（热点为：</span><span class="stl_29 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">SS700_XXXXXX</span><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">，默认 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 27.5062em; left:9.5434em;z-index:463; "><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_30">密码为：</span><span class="stl_29 stl_08 stl_30">88888888</span><span class="stl_28 stl_08 stl_30">）， &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 31.0114em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09">2-4-1</span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_09">、</span><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_09">PPPoE &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 33.2995em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">在管理后台点击</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">外网配置</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">&gt;</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">有线</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">，在</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">协议</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">上选择</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">“PPPoE </span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">拨号</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_31" style="word-spacing:-0.0572em;">，输入相应上网账号和密码进行 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 34.5995em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_09">保存，再“点击生效”。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 42.9161em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_09">配置成功后，显示的具体信息如下图： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 58.5447em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_32" style="word-spacing:-0.0243em;">2-4-2</span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_32" style="word-spacing:-0.0243em;">、</span><span class="stl_18 stl_08 stl_32" style="word-spacing:-0.0243em;">WiFi </span><span class="stl_19 stl_08 stl_32" style="word-spacing:-0.0243em;">中继 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 60.8328em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">在管理后台点击</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_33">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">外网配置</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_33">&gt;WiFi”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">，扫描后选择要中继的路由并输入密码进行保存，再</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_33">“</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">点击生效</span><span class="stl_15 stl_08 stl_33">”</span><span class="stl_11 stl_08 stl_33">。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 67.8495em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_22 stl_08 stl_09">配置成功后，显示的具体信息如下图： &nbsp;</span></div>
